Popular Nigerian comedian and brand ambassador, Samuel Animashaun Perry, also known as Broda Shaggi, is one of the most talented and hardworking comic actors in the country.
Recently, Broda Shaggi sparked a flurry of reactions on social media from Obi Cubana and other fans after he took to the Instagram feed with some new, stunningly captured photos of himself. In the photos, Broda Shaggi can be seen shirtless while being tied with a wrapper, a crown on his head, and adorning himself with beads, depicting a perfect picture of an African king. He looked really cute and got into the outfit. The humorist shared the photos today on his verified Instagram page. Take a look at the photos shared below.

While releasing the photos online, he added a caption that reads, “Odogwu you bad.”
A few moments ago after the photos surfaced online, Obi Cubana, a renowned billionaire businessman, and several other fans quickly rushed down to the comment box section to express their reactions from different perspectives.
